56/answer","Biography information for Lucy Frazer","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/857756/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/857756/answer",,,,,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2018-03-08","Prisons: Vocational Guidance","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, what provisions are planned to be in place from 1 April 2018 to provide prisoners with independent careers advice at the start of their sentence.","false","Biography information for Imran Hussain","Bradford East","Imran Hussain","131657"
