"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/857814","Department for Transport","false","2018-03-13","<p>The Department for Transport consists of a central department and four executive agencies as follows:</p><p> </p><p>Government Car Service (GCS) a division of the central department.</p><p>Driver &amp; Vehicle Licensing Agency (DVLA)</p><p>Driver &amp; Vehicle Standards Agency (DVSA)</p><p>Maritime &amp; Coastguard Agency (MCA)</p><p>Vehicle Certification Agency (VCA)</p><p> </p><p>The table below lists how many vehicles are in each fleet with totals for (a) owned and (b) leased:</p><p><strong> </strong></p><table><tbody><tr><td><p> </p></td><td><p><strong>Owned</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Leased</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>GCS</strong></p></td><td><p>89</p></td><td><p>5</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>DVSA</strong></p></td><td><p>329</p></td><td><p>846</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>DVLA</strong></p></td><td><p>1</p></td><td><p>25</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>MCA</strong></p></td><td><p>429</p></td><td><p>0</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>VCA</strong></p></td><td><p>13</p></td><td><p>2</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong> </strong></p></td><td><p> </p></td><td><p> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Totals</strong></p></td><td><p>861</p></td><td><p>878</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong> </strong></p><p><strong> </strong></p><p> </p><p> </p>","Wealden","Ms Nusrat Ghani",,"2018-03-13T17:21:09.113Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/857814/answer","Biography information for Ms Nusrat Ghani","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/857814/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/857814/answer",,,,,,,,"27","Transport","Transport","2018-03-08","Department for Transport: Motor Vehicles","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Transport, how many vehicles his Department (a) owns and (b) leases.","false","Biography information for Mary Creagh","Wakefield","Mary Creagh","131715"
